pd_0_com_0text: Hey, I'm new in town. My name's [PName]. what is there to do for fun around here?
pd_0_com_1text: You'll have to excuse me. I have trouble ignoring such alluring people.
pd_0_com_2text: Hey, I'm... I mean, uhh, you'll... never mind.
pd_1_com_0text: Oh, hello. I am Strannik. I don't know much about this town, I simply eat and wander.
pd_2_com_0text: I have noticed the nearby dungeons just off of the town.
pd_3_com_0text: I hit things with my halberd, I go where there are sights to see, and it is tough to take me down.
pd_4_com_0text: Then why are you here? Oh, you mean... me? Well, I am Strannik.
pd_5_com_0text: You sound like a valuable ally. I could use your help exploring the dungeons if you'd assist me?
pd_6_com_0text: I care little for money, but food is important. I will follow you if you promise such things.
pd_7_com_0text: If the rumours are true, the monsters that dwell within them have even been posing a threat to the village.
pd_8_com_0text: If I see to it to venture into the dungeons would you be able to help me? It's dangerous to go alone after all.
pd_11_com_1text: Tell me something from your past
pd_11_com_2text: Tell me about your likes / dislikes
pd_12_com_0text: There is not much to tell, but I will try.
pd_13_com_0text: Could you tell me something about yourself?
pd_var_14_0: I found this harp during my travels. I am no good at playing it, but it's nice to listen to.
pd_var_14_1: I have wandered the lands for so long, it has become natural to me. There is a whole world to see, so I might as well go see it
pd_var_14_2: I sharpen my halberd when there is nothing else to do. You never know when a fight may happen.
pd_15_com_0text: How do you feel about us?
pd_18_com_0text: I wouldn't mind wandering with you.
pd_19_com_0text: We make a great fellowship, [PName]. If going gets tough, you call Strannik.
pd_20_com_0text: Where are you from? What brought you here?
pd_21_com_0text: I did not belong where I was. That is all I will say.
pd_22_com_0text: I never knew my birth family. I wander to find where I belong.
pd_23_com_0text: I was orphaned to lizardfolk, and don't know who I was born to. Maybe I'll find them one day.
pd_24_com_0text: I never knew my true parents when I was young. I grew up with lizardfolk, who raised me and taught me the value of kindness. I care about them, but I feel I could not connect with them. If I don't belong with the lizardfolk or my real family, then I will wander, for I do not belong anywhere.
pd_25_com_0text: What do you like? What do you hate?
pd_var_26_0: I like to eat Steak. Tough to chew, filling, and straight forward, just how a fight should be
pd_var_26_1: I hate beans. They are too small. Why should food be small? It makes no sense.
pd_var_26_2: I love to see the sky, that blue azure on a clear day is my favourite colour.
pd_27_com_0text: What can you tell me about your abilities?
pd_30_com_0text: This is… very tasty. Thank you.
pd_31_com_0text: I don’t understand this, [PName]. But it is pretty.
pd_32_com_0text: I cannot read this. It looks pretty though.
pd_33_com_0text: These shoes… they are too tight. But they have spikes, still a useful throwing weapon.
pd_34_com_0text: Something for my halberd? You have my thanks, [PName]!
pd_35_com_0text: These taste… okay... I will eat them. Thanks, [PName].
pd_36_com_0text: I cannot read. Fancy writing looks nice, though.
pd_37_com_0text: This small weapon makes funny jokes. Heh.
pd_38_com_0text: You care about my scales…? This does not happen much… It is very nice of you, [PName]!
pd_42_com_0text: How about this? Whatever you find in the dungeon, you get to keep.
pd_42_com_1text: Sorry, I have nothing to offer you
pd_44_com_0text: I suppose I could trade loot for food...
pd_45_com_0text: We have good times. You are good company.
pd_46_com_0text: I really enjoyed spending time with you. We sure make a great team.
pd_46_com_1text: Are you a sorcerer because your beauty is inate.
pd_47_com_0text: I know little about magic. You confuse me, [PName].
pd_48_com_0text: You are very reliable. We work well together, I think.
pd_49_com_0text: We have been through so much together now.
pd_49_com_1text: You and I are a natural crit, how about we take things to the next level?
pd_50_com_0text: This journey has been a valuable one. I like hearing your voice.
pd_51_com_0text: Yes. I think so too. I consider you a friend.
pd_52_com_0text: I really feel like we get along famously.
pd_52_com_1text: You must be a rogue with high dexterity, because you've stolen my heart.
pd_53_com_0text: I do not usually enjoy company, [PName], but... you are nice to be around. Let us wander.
